                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <desc>
                              <locus target="#iir(ecto)" facs="002">Fol. iir(ecto)</locus> Will of <foreign xml:lang="gez">እመሆይ፡ ደስተ፡ አዛገ፡</foreign>
